resources.name: update Item
resources.description:
Param ItemID is the name of the item, trimed and spaces replaced with underscores

```
	"context_type": "items" //"items", "modifier_items"
```
context_type `items` will modify the items with the specified data
context_type `modifier_items` will modify the modifeir items (add-ons) with the specified data

so when you want to update an item or a group, you place them new data to be updated as it is specified in the upload menu
